     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><div xml:lang=\"fr-FR\" lang=\"fr-FR\"><hr/><p><b>French (France)</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narratif généré : CarteDeConcepts PN13-FHIR-prescmed-medicationcomp-conceptmap</b></p><a name=\"PN13-FHIR-prescmed-medicationcomp-conceptmap\"> </a><a name=\"hcPN13-FHIR-prescmed-medicationcomp-conceptmap\"> </a><p>Mapping de https://interopsante.org/pn13/xsd vers <a href=\"StructureDefinition-fr-medication-compound.html\">FR Medication Compound</a></p><br/><p>Mapping de <code>terminologie de référence (CodeSystem) non spécifiée</code> to <code>terminologie de référence (CodeSystem) non spécifiée</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><b>Détails du concept source</b></td><td><b>relation</b></td><td colspan=\"3\"><b>Détails du concept cible</b></td><td><b>Commentaire</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><b>Codes</b> de </td><td><b>Forme@Phastnomenclature</b></td><td/><td colspan=\"2\"><b>Codes</b> de </td><td><b>Medication.form.coding.system</b></td><td/></tr><tr><td style=\"border-right-width: 0px\">Messages/M_prescription_médicaments/Prescription/Elément_prescr_médic/Forme</td><td style=\"border-left-width: 0px\"/><td>SIPh-CIO_Forme</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td style=\"border-right-width: 0px\">Medication.form.coding.code</td><td style=\"border-left-width: 0px\"/><td/><td>le code cible est à trouver dans le mapping Free Set CIO-DC FORME</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-right-width: 0px\"/><td style=\"border-left-width: 0px\"/><td>{Absent}</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td style=\"border-right-width: 0px\">Medication.form.coding.code</td><td style=\"border-left-width: 0px\"/><td/><td>le code cible est à trouver dans le mapping Free Set CIO-DC FORME</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-right-width: 0px\"/><td style=\"border-left-width: 0px\"/><td>EDQM</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equal\" title=\"equal\">is equal to</a></td><td style=\"border-right-width: 0px\">Medication.form.coding.code</td><td style=\"border-left-width: 0px\"/><td>http://standardterms.edqm.eu</td><td/></tr><tr><td style=\"border-right-width: 0px\"/><td style=\"border-left-width: 0px\"/><td>SIPh-Forme</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#relatedto\" title=\"relatedto\">is related to</a></td><td style=\"border-right-width: 0px\">Medication.form.coding.code</td><td style=\"border-left-width: 0px\"/><td/><td>Certains codes cibles peuvent être trouvés dans le mapping Free Set CIO-DC FORME. Dans le cas contraire, si la traduction en EDQM n'est pas possible, Medication.form.text peut être utilisé mais pourrait poser des problèmes d'interprétation</td></tr></table></div><div xml:lang=\"en\" lang=\"en\"><hr/><p><b>English</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ConceptMap PN13-FHIR-prescmed-medicationcomp-conceptmap</b></p><a name=\"en-PN13-FHIR-prescmed-medicationcomp-conceptmap\"> </a><a name=\"en-hcPN13-FHIR-prescmed-medicationcomp-conceptmap\"> </a><p>Mapping from https://interopsante.org/pn13/xsd to <a href=\"StructureDefinition-fr-medication-compound.html\">FR Medication Compound</a></p><br/><p>Mapping from <code>unspecified code system</code> to <code>unspecified code system</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><b>Source Concept Details</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td colspan=\"3\"><b>Target Concept Details</b></td><td><b>Comment</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><b>Codes</b> from </td><td><b>Forme@Phastnomenclature</b></td><td/><td colspan=\"2\"><b>Codes</b> from </td><td><b>Medication.form.coding.system</b></td><td/></tr><tr><td style=\"border-right-width: 0px\">Messages/M_prescription_médicaments/Prescription/Elément_prescr_médic/Forme</td><td style=\"border-left-width: 0px\"/><td>SIPh-CIO_Forme</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td style=\"border-right-width: 0px\">Medication.form.coding.code</td><td style=\"border-left-width: 0px\"/><td/><td>le code cible est à trouver dans le mapping Free Set CIO-DC FORME</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-right-width: 0px\"/><td style=\"border-left-width: 0px\"/><td>{Absent}</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td style=\"border-right-width: 0px\">Medication.form.coding.code</td><td style=\"border-left-width: 0px\"/><td/><td>le code cible est à trouver dans le mapping Free Set CIO-DC FORME</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-right-width: 0px\"/><td style=\"border-left-width: 0px\"/><td>EDQM</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equal\" title=\"equal\">is equal to</a></td><td style=\"border-right-width: 0px\">Medication.form.coding.code</td><td style=\"border-left-width: 0px\"/><td>http://standardterms.edqm.eu</td><td/></tr><tr><td style=\"border-right-width: 0px\"/><td style=\"border-left-width: 0px\"/><td>SIPh-Forme</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#relatedto\" title=\"relatedto\">is related to</a></td><td style=\"border-right-width: 0px\">Medication.form.coding.code</td><td style=\"border-left-width: 0px\"/><td/><td>Certains codes cibles peuvent être trouvés dans le mapping Free Set CIO-DC FORME. Dans le cas contraire, si la traduction en EDQM n'est pas possible, Medication.form.text peut être utilisé mais pourrait poser des problèmes d'interprétation</td></tr></table></div></div>"
